name: Folded Circle: Master Edition
description:
Folded was originally minted on fxhash on 28/12/2021 as an edition of 100 unique generative tokens. This master edition includes all 100 unique tokens.

Inspired by hard-edge painters from the 1960s, a collection of colourful geometries.

Unique generative properties include colour palettes, number of stripes, number of folds, colour sequence.

https://www.fxhash.xyz/generative/3760

JPG, 8000x8000 px

 Made with code and love by AutoEclectus in Australia.

 AutoEclectus is a visual artist specialising in code-based generative works.
